# writing long papers
## grow seeds
start by writing bullet points, then turn them into small sentences, then grow them into longer paragraphs

# A mountain of work
## All ur evenings are belong to us
As soon as you get home, crack open your assignments and continuously work on
them as you do all your other home-related things. Always have a book or 
assignment open. This means you'll be chipping away at your workload constantly.
